h%E1%BA%A3i/Thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i/poem-GfhLycCKcIYsbSecM0pJiA">Thuật hoài - 述懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ph%C3%B9ng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-0stQjCT1gq_a6xH28mb1ow">Tương phùng hành - 相逢行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/Y%C3%AAn-ca-h%C3%A0nh-k%E1%BB%B3-2-Bi%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-Kc8R88uruzsjyzzUopw4VQ">Yên ca hành kỳ 2 - Biệt nhật - 燕歌行其二－別日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
